text: This Earth Is Mine is a 1959 American drama movie directed by Henry King and starring Rock Hudson, Jean Simmons, Dorothy McGuire, Claude Rains, Kent Smith, Anna Lee, Geraldine Wall. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1959 drama movies Category:1950s American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Henry King
title: This Earth Is Mine (1959 movie)
